name: EnergyTrade Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
ETT is an ESG (Environmental / Social / Governance) token built on Hedera. It will allow monitoring / auditing of energy usage and trading for Enterprise. ETT is an HTS-based token.

ETT is a commodity for driving out network capability, and not as security.
